section.p:
You can also add CTHs within a test suite. This is done by returning {ct_hooks,[CTH]} in the config list from suite/0,
init_per_suite/1 or
init_per_group/2. CTH in this case can be either only the module name of the CTH or a tuple with the module name and the initial arguments and optionally the hook priority of the CTH. Eg: {ct_hooks,[my_cth_module]} or {ct_hooks,[{my_cth_module,[{debug,true}]}]} or {ct_hooks,[{my_cth_module,[{debug,true}],500}]}
